Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP14.client.view.cli

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UIColor
    Interface representing a color for the UI.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CLI
    A Command Line Interface implementation of the UI.
    CLIHelper
    Class that contains utility to draw better Command Line Interfaces.
    ColorChar
    A class that offers a way to concatenate a char with a color escape sequence.
    GodFactory
    Returns GodModel instances found in the godsFile.
    UICache
    This class reproduce locally the basic features of the server in order to maintain a consistent state of the game between server and client.
    UICell
    A class that represent a cell on the board.
    UIGod
    Implementation of the GodModel.
    UIPlayer
    Class containing all the details that are useful client-side to display a player, in addition to their workers.
    UIWorker
    Represent a Worker and all of its binding to the owner (Player) and a board cell.
